    "en_q": "A company hosts a Windows-based file server on a fleet of Amazon EC2 instances across multiple Availability Zones. The current setup does not allow application servers to access files simultaneously from the EC2 fleet. Which solution will allow this access in the MOST operationally efficient way?",
